  <description>
    <p>Maxint is an <em>open-banking</em> Mint alternative.</p>
    <p>Sign up with 2FA, link your bank accounts, enrich transactions, craft budgets, get bill notifications and find best banks to maximize your interest.</p>
    <p>A list of features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Link any bank, catch account fees</li>
      <li>Track your wealth, boost financial health</li>
      <li>Tag your transactions, personalize finances</li>
      <li>Optimize your expenses, maximize savings</li>
      <li>Tailor budget to your needs, wants and goals</li>
      <li>Monitor inflation, protect your purchasing power</li>
      <li>Explore high-yield offers, maximize your interest</li>
      <li>Compare credit card rewards, based on your spending</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
